	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In the SMB2 disassembly by Beneficii, There are 4 switches of data:<br /><br />MAIN (also, Level Data and Sound Engine part 1),<br />DATA2 (game over, etc.),<br />DATA3 (Levels part two, etc.)<br />DATA4 (Ending, Sound Engine 2, etc.)<br /><br />Get it from Gil Galid's Game Source Code Website (Onyxite seems to be the ALT name of Beneficii?):<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://gilgalad.arc-nova.org/vgscr/fds/smb2.zip">http://gilgalad.arc-nova.org/vgscr/fds/smb2.zip</a><!-- m -->

		

